review_blob: I love this beer!!  Had it in a bar in Tel Aviv, Israel.  Very dark with medium head and a sweet AND slightly bitter aftertaste.  My favorite dark lager.  Here is my plea and I know it belongs in the forums.  I cant get this beer in the U.S.!  Email me at cannetti@gmail.com and we can work something out it you can get it in your country.  Thanks and regards to all fellow beer lovers.
